'''Kindle Fire'''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0051VVOB2 |title=Kindle Fire: Full Color Kindle with 7" Multi-Touch Display, Wi-Fi |work=[[Amazon.com|Amazon.com]] |accessdate=28 September 2011 |publisher=Amazon.com, Inc |archive-date=2020-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120053906/http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0051VVOB2 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 是一款由[[亞馬遜公司|亞馬遜公司]]於2011年9月28日推出的[[平板電腦|平板電腦]]，屬於[[Amazon_Kindle|Kindle]][[電子書|電子書]]閱覽器系列產品。Kindle Fire擁有一片七[[英寸|英寸]]的[[多點觸控|多點觸控式]][[电容式感应|電容]][[觸控式螢幕|觸控式螢幕]]，該螢幕採用了[[橫向電場效應顯示技術|IPS]]材質。Kindle Fire的正面面積為7.5 × 4.7吋，可視[[屏幕|屏幕]]面積為4 × 6吋。Kindle Fire還搭載了一個由亞馬遜深度定制的[[Google|Google]] [[Android|Android]]操作系統。該系統內置了亞馬遜的服務，包含亞馬遜電子商店、媒體電影、在線電視和Kindle系列的在線電子書。

Kindle Fire於2011年11月中旬首先在[[美國|美國]]發售，上市售價為$199[[美元|美元]]<ref name="ChiTrib">{{cite news |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/business/breaking/chi-amazon-unveiling-new-tablet-today-its-challenge-to-the-ipad-20110928,0,2380818.story |title=Amazon's Kindle Fire tablet to sell at $199, challenging iPad |date=28 September 2011 |work=[[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928174646/http://www.chicagotribune.com/business/breaking/chi-amazon-unveiling-new-tablet-today-its-challenge-to-the-ipad-20110928,0,2380818.story |archivedate=2011年9月28日 |accessdate=2011年10月20日 }}</ref>。

2012年8月的市場調查報告顯示，在Kindle Fire停止銷售之前，該型裝置在美國市場的市占率約為22%<ref>[http://www.boston.com/business/technology/2012/08/30/amazon-kindle-fire-sold-out-new-model-expected/9mXIGxRBStTZuRcB4uZccM/story.html Amazon Kindle Fire sold out as new model expected] {{Wayback|url=http://www.boston.com/business/technology/2012/08/30/amazon-kindle-fire-sold-out-new-model-expected/9mXIGxRBStTZuRcB4uZccM/story.html |date=20120901222330 }}, Boston.com</ref>，同時間iPad的市占率則下滑至約50%。<ref>[http://www.latimes.com/business/technology/la-fi-tn-ipad-market-share-falls-20120731,0,7577986.story iPad market share falls according to survey] {{Wayback|url=http://www.latimes.com/business/technology/la-fi-tn-ipad-market-share-falls-20120731,0,7577986.story |date=20120823192539 }}, LA Times,  02 AUG 2012</ref><ref>[http://blogs.smartmoney.com/paydirt/2012/08/02/is-kindle-fire-burning-the-ipad/?link=SM_hp_ls4e Is Kindle Fire Burning the iPad?] {{Wayback|url=http://blogs.smartmoney.com/paydirt/2012/08/02/is-kindle-fire-burning-the-ipad/?link=SM_hp_ls4e |date=20160305040319 }}, Quentin Fottrell, blogs.smartmoney.com</ref><ref>[http://www.minyanville.com/business-news/editors-pick/articles/amazon-kindle-fire-amzn-goog-aapl/8/30/2012/id/43621 Did Amazon Fudge Its 22% Market Share Number for the Kindle Fire?] {{Wayback|url=http://www.minyanville.com/business-news/editors-pick/articles/amazon-kindle-fire-amzn-goog-aapl/8/30/2012/id/43621 |date=20120901032147 }}, Michael Comeau, Aug 30 2012, www.minyanville.com</ref>

==設計==
Kindle Fire擁有自己的用戶界面，該用戶界面基於[[Google|Google]]的[[Android|Android]] 2.3薑餅操作系統<ref>{{cite news |url=http://thisismynext.com/2011/09/28/amazon-android-ui-kindle-fire-ux/ |title=Amazon’s Kindle Fire UI: it’s Android, but not quite |first=Sean |last=Hollister |date=28 September 2011 |work=This Is My Next |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111031032335/http://thisismynext.com/2011/09/28/amazon-android-ui-kindle-fire-ux/ |archivedate=2011年10月31日 |accessdate=2011年10月20日 }}</ref>。內部採用一顆1GHz [[OMAP|德州儀器OMAP]]4代的[[雙核處理器|雙核處理器]]，觸控螢幕分辨率為1024×600，大小為七英寸，與之前的亞馬遜Kindle產品不同的是Kindle Fire的螢幕是彩色的。

聯外裝置支持[[802.11n|802.11n]]和[[Wi-Fi|Wi-Fi]]無線網路，以及[[USB_2.0|USB 2.0]]連接埠，並且內置8GB的儲存空間，但沒有記憶卡插槽可擴充空間。官方宣稱Kindle Fire的儲存空間可以支持用戶安裝80多個應用程式、超過十部高畫質電影、800首[[MP3|MP3]]或6,000多部電子書<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.engadget.com/2011/09/28/amazon-fire-tablet-unveiled-7-inch-display-199-price-tag/ |title=Amazon Kindle Fire tablet unveiled: Android-based, 7-inch display, $199 price tag |first=Darren |last=Murph |date=28 September 2011 |work=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |publisher=AOL Inc |accessdate=2011-10-20 |archive-date=2019-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191017060505/https://www.engadget.com/2011/09/28/amazon-fire-tablet-unveiled-7-inch-display-199-price-tag/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://thisismynext.com/2011/09/28/amazon-kindle-fire-vs-ipad-2-vs-nook-color-numbers |title=Amazon Kindle Fire vs. iPad 2 vs. Nook Color: by the numbers |first=Chris |last=Ziegler |date=28 September 2011 |work=This Is My Next |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110930111558/http://thisismynext.com/2011/09/28/amazon-kindle-fire-vs-ipad-2-vs-nook-color-numbers/ |archivedate=2011年9月30日 |accessdate=2011年10月20日 }}</ref>。

Kindle Fire還內置了Amazon Appstore{{r|spec1}}，以及一個使用[[Amazon_EC2|Amazon EC2]]技術的雲端瀏覽器[[Amazon_Silk|Amazon Silk]]和其他亞馬遜服務<ref>{{citation| url = http://www.eweekeurope.co.uk/news/amazon-ec2-underlies-kindle-tablet-silk-browser-40927| title = Amazon EC2 Underlies Kindle Tablet 'Silk' Browser| date = 29 September 2011| author = Clint Boulton| work = www.eweekeurope.co.uk| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111005152446/http://www.eweekeurope.co.uk/news/amazon-ec2-underlies-kindle-tablet-silk-browser-40927| archivedate = 2011年10月5日| accessdate = 2011年10月20日}}</ref><ref>{{citation| url = http://www.amazon.com/gp/help/customer/display.html/ref=hp_rel_topic?ie=UTF8&nodeId=200775440| title = Amazon.com Help: Amazon Silk| work = www.amazon.com| publisher = [[Amazon.com|Amazon.com]]| accessdate = 2 October 2011| archive-date = 2020-07-25| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200725062154/https://www.amazon.com/gp/help/customer/display.html/ref=hp_rel_topic?ie=UTF8&nodeId=200775440| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{citation| url = http://amazonsilk.wordpress.com/2011/09/28/introducing-amazon-silk/| title = Introducing Amazon Silk| date = 28 September 2011| author = 'Amazon Silk team'| work = amazonsilk.wordpress.com| 6 = | deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120705154238/http://amazonsilk.wordpress.com/2011/09/28/introducing-amazon-silk/| archivedate = 2012年7月5日| accessdate = 2011年10月20日}}</ref>。用戶可以利用內置的亞馬遜[[雲端儲存|雲端儲存]]服務額外獲得更大的儲存空間{{r|spec1}}，且內置的[[電子郵件|電子郵件]]應用服務可以允許用戶使用所有商業郵箱和其他電子郵箱，例如[[Gmail|Gmail]]、[[Yahoo!_Mail|Yahoo!]]、[[Hotmail|Hotmail]]、[[AOL_Mail|AOL Mail]]等等，並能隨時隨地獲取郵件{{r|spec1}}。

Kindle Fire可支持[[AZW|.azw]]、[[.txt|TXT]]、[[.pdf|PDF]]、[[MOBI|MOBI]]、[[Audible.com|Audible]]（Audible Enhanced (AA, AAX)）、[[.doc|DOC]]、[[.docx|DOCX]]、[[.jpeg|JPEG]]、[[.gif|GIF]]、[[.png|PNG]]、[[.bmp|BMP]]、non-DRM [[.aac|AAC]]、[[.mp3|MP3]]、[[MIDI|MIDI]]、[[.ogg|OGG]]、[[.wav|WAV]]、[[.mp4|MP4]]、[[VP8|VP8]]<ref name="spec1">{{citation| url = http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0051VVOB2| title = Kindle Fire - the Amazon Tablet with Full Color 7" Multi-Touch Display, Wi-Fi| work = www.amazon.com| publisher = [[Amazon.com|Amazon.com]]| accessdate = 2 October| archive-date = 2020-11-20| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201120053906/http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0051VVOB2| dead-url = no}}</ref>等多種格式文件。

